contentrichtext.text: '''OBL''' may refer to: * Obol Basketball League, former name for the [[Swedish Basketball League]] * [[Osama bin Laden]] (1957–2011), founder of the al-Qaeda militiant organization * [[Zoersel-Oostmalle Airfield]], IATA code '''ÖBL''' may refer to: * [[Österreichische Basketball Bundesliga]], the top men's professional basketball league in Austria * [[Österreichisches Biographisches Lexikon 1815–1950]], a biographical dictionary of individuals who've contributed to the history of Austria {{disambiguation}}
